      <title>法国富人有望因增税而退出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/wealthy-french-seen-edging-toward-the-exits-on-tax-increases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财富和税务顾问表示，法国首相米歇尔·巴尼耶 (Michel Barnier) 提高富人税收的计划可能会导致一些人搬出法国，而其他原本考虑在法国定居的人则取消计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/wealthy-french-seen-edging-toward-the-exits-on-tax-increases</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 04:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国首富因合并赢得投资者青睐而财富倍增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/richest-thai-widens-wealth-lead-as-investors-favor-energy-telecom-firms-merger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着能源与电信部门合并接近完成，萨拉特·拉塔纳瓦迪的盈利潜力进一步增强，他的财富也随之增加，进一步巩固了其泰国首富的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/richest-thai-widens-wealth-lead-as-investors-favor-energy-telecom-firms-merger</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 03:20:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴菲特将美国银行股份减持至 10% 以下，以便秘密进行交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/buffett-cuts-bofa-stake-below-10-letting-him-trade-in-secret</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃伦·巴菲特 (Warren Buffett) 现在可以慢慢披露其在美国银行公司的股票交易情况，因为他的企业集团所持的股份已被削减至低于 10% 的监管门槛，而该门槛要求他迅速披露。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/buffett-cuts-bofa-stake-below-10-letting-him-trade-in-secret</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 22:19:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国货币市场基金积压资金达创纪录的 6.47 万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/a-record-6-47-trillion-is-piling-up-in-us-money-market-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[面对美联储降息，投资者纷纷涌入美国货币市场基金，推动该行业的总资产达到创纪录的 6.47 万亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/a-record-6-47-trillion-is-piling-up-in-us-money-market-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 19:44:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为什么你会觉得工作很困难——以及你能做些什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-10-10/how-to-change-your-job-career-experts-explain-why-workers-are-feeling-stuck</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果你现在觉得自己的职业生涯陷入了困境，那你并不孤单——经济学家表示，劳动力市场的当前趋势让有抱负的专业人士很容易陷入停滞。幸运的是，你可以采取一些策略来解决这个问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-10-10/how-to-change-your-job-career-experts-explain-why-workers-are-feeling-stuck</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 17:00:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2025 年美国退休人员社会保障金将增加 2.5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/us-retirees-to-get-2-5-boost-to-social-security-checks-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2025年，约7250万美国人的退休金或伤残津贴每月将增加2.5%，由于通胀进一步放缓，这一调整幅度小于今年他们所获得的福利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/us-retirees-to-get-2-5-boost-to-social-security-checks-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 13:08:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
